---
title: Mushroom, Tomato & Basil Pesto Risotto with Pear Salad & Almonds
description: Keep warm with an expertly cooked and flavoured risotto (in case it wasn’t clear, you’re the expert!). Hearty and homey, the earthen taste of the mushrooms blended with a tomato sauce and topped with basil pesto, come together to create a risotto that has everyone humming with bliss.
